<html lang='en'>
  <head>
    <meta charset='UTF-8' />
    <meta name='viewport' content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0' />
    <title>Password Reset</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>Hello {{userName}},</p>
    <br />
    <p>We received a request to reset your password for your account associated
      with this email address. If you did not make this request, please ignore
      this email.</p>
    <p>
      To reset your password, please click the link here:
      <a href='{{resetLink}}'>Reset your password</a></p>
    <br />
    <p>This link will expire in 30 minutes. If you encounter any issues, please
      contact our support team.</p>

    <br />
    <p>Thank you, </p>
    <p>{{appName}} Team</p>
    <br />
    <br />
    <small>Disclaimer: If you did not request a password reset, please ensure
      your account's security and contact our support team immediately.</small>
  </body>
</html>